token_info.name: Joker 2 - Deck of Demise
token_info.description: Joker #2 (of 2) in the "Deck of Demise" series. These NFTs will be given to all addresses which hold a straight flush of "Deck of Demise" NFTs and will not be sold. This NFT appears as an unedited, uninscribed, playing card, though there is a hidden inscription. See OBJKT 36050 for series details.
